data.text:
Our comic book divider labels are printed on high quality adhesive vinyl. They are sized to fit dividers like BCW Comic Book Dividers andMax Pro Comic Dividers, and fit most other dividers available. Dimensions: 3 1/2 x 5/8 inch

Available in 2 finishes:

Standard - Our durable, high quality label with a semi-gloss finish that is a great addition to your collection.

Laminated - The standard label layered with a glossy laminate for the highest protection and scratch proofing. Recommended for more frequently flipped through dividers like in a comic shop or convention setup.

Processing time for most orders is 10 to 14 days. Larger orders may take longer. Custom label requests lengthen processing times as we take care to design and layout each label. We print and cut labels in batches and do our best to get them to you in a timely manner. Should a delay arise, we will email as soon as possible.

Labels are mailed in a semi-rigid cardboard mailer through USPS without tracking info. Shipping upgrades with tracking information are available at checkout.
